org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML
Interface LidarSystem

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ObjectDetectionSensorSystem, ObjectTrackingSensorSystem, RoboticSystem, SensorSystem, System
All Known Implementing Classes:
LidarSystemImpl
public interface LidarSystem
extends ObjectDetectionSensorSystem, ObjectTrackingSensorSystem

A representation of the model object 'Lidar System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Nb Layers
  • Layer Angle Min
  • Layer Angle Step
  • Noise
  • Sigma Noise
  • Angle min
  • Angle max
  • Time increment
  • Scan time
  • Range min
  • Range max

See Also:
RobotMLPackage.getLidarSystem()
